        public int fitnessLevel
        VO2max fitness level can be expressed directly as a VO2max value in ml/kg/min (range ~15-80ml/kg/min), but that value probably does not tell a lot for any consumer. Typically VO2max fitness level is scaled and shown for individual as a comparison to reference group for same age and gender from 1 to 7. @See FitnessLevel
